---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Keep Choosing Good"
  description="Learn about Keep Choosing Good and our mission to inspire positive change"
>
  <main>
    <article class="about-page">
      <div class="container">
        <header class="page-header">
          <h1>About Keep Choosing Good</h1>
          <p class="lead">Our mission is to inspire and empower individuals to make positive choices every day</p>
        </header>

        <section class="content">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>
            Keep Choosing Good began with a simple belief: every choice we make has the power to create positive change,
            no matter how small. In a world filled with challenges, we wanted to create a space that encourages and
            celebrates the decision to choose good.
          </p>

          <h2>What We Believe</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Every person has the power to make a positive impact</li>
            <li>Small, consistent choices lead to meaningful change</li>
            <li>Community and support amplify our individual efforts</li>
            <li>Authenticity and compassion guide our actions</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Join Us</h2>
          <p>
            Whether you're looking for inspiration, resources, or a community of like-minded individuals,
            Keep Choosing Good is here to support your journey. Together, we can create a ripple effect of
            positive change that extends far beyond ourselves.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .content li {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .content li::before {
    content: 'âœ“';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
</style>
